# CRM System

## Description
Full-stack CRM system to manage leads, customers, and sales pipeline using React, Node.js, and MongoDB.

## Features
- Add new leads
- View leads in table
- REST API integration
- MongoDB database storage

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React.js
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js
- Database: MongoDB

## How to Run
1. Start backend:
   cd server
   npm install
   node server.js

2. Start frontend:
   cd client
   npm install
   npm start

